  "description": "\u003Cdiv class='descriptionContainer'\u003E    \u003Cdiv class='pdpRow'\u003E        \u003Cdiv class='productText'\u003E            \u003Ch3\u003E                Clean and Simple            \u003C/h3\u003E            \u003Cp\u003E                The Battery Shield is both a stylish trim panel which provides a clean look to your engine bay and a                solid protective cover for your battery. The quick release latches give the shield race car aesthetic                and functionality. It also makes for a decent spot to slap on some stickers if you are looking for a                performance boost.            \u003C/p\u003E        \u003C/div\u003E        \u003Cdiv class='productGraphic'\u003E            \u003Cimg alt='Battery Shield Quick Release Infographic'                src='https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-351ed/product_images/uploaded_images/nd-miata-battery-shield-quick-release-graphic.png' /\u003E        \u003C/div\u003E    \u003C/div\u003E    \u003Cdiv class='pdpRow reversed'\u003E        \u003Cdiv class='productText'\u003E            \u003Ch3\u003E                High Quality Materials            \u003C/h3\u003E            \u003Cp\u003E                Skimping on materials is not really in our vocabulary. The cover is precision machined from a high                quality plastic called Hydex 1050. The racing inspired quick release latches pair with custom made                stainless steel standoffs to provide the ultimate convenience when the cover needs to be removed. For                added stability, we have installed padding on the under side of the cover.            \u003C/p\u003E            \u003Ch3\u003E                Function and Compatibility            \u003C/h3\u003E            \u003Cp\u003E                To remove the cover, simply depress the two quick release buttons and lift up. Installing it is even                easier, just align each release over it's mounting point and press the cover down until it snaps into                place. The standoffs install in place of the OEM battery tie-down nuts. The shield is compatible with                either the OEM tie-down, or our                \u003Ca class='descriptionLink' href='/battery-tie-down-for-nd-miata/'\u003E                    custom billet tie-down                \u003C/a\u003E            \u003C/p\u003E        \u003C/div\u003E        \u003Cdiv class='productGraphic'\u003E            \u003Cimg alt='Battery Shield rendering'                src='https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-351ed/product_images/uploaded_images/nd-miata-battery-shield-graphic.png' /\u003E        \u003C/div\u003E    \u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E",
